    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You collect a misterious energy into a ball, and shoot it towards a target, making every move into a pain. Make ranged genjutsu attack against a creature you can see within range, dealing 4d4 psychic damage on a hit and forcing the target to make an intelligence saving throw:</p><ul><li><strong>Success</strong>: No effect.</li><li><strong>Failure</strong>: Until the start of your next turn, when the targed would take an action, bonus action, or reaction, it takes 1d4 psychic damage.</li><li><strong>Critical Failure</strong>: As a failure, but the damage die becomes d6.</li></ul><p><strong>At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank above D-rank, increase this jutsu's cost by 3, and the damage on a hit by 1d4. Starting at B-rank, the damage on a failed save increases by 1 die. Starting at S-rank, the damage on a failed save increases by 2 dice.</p>",
